{"tid":990362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府被指私助建制派政黨，優先取得大批4000蚊申請表","createTime":"2019-01-21T13:42:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T14:01:18.000Z","uid":36901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2c135d14cb5a3138ff2db8bdd23f0a729ab7ec5d","tid":990362,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:42:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190121/59167210\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190121%2F59167210&d=1L79tNmClEUrvu3H0gBFjDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=ec6d76a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190121%2F59167210&h=5a5ac737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190121/59167210</a><br />\n<br />\n政府被指私助建制派政黨，優先取得大批申請表，對民主派政黨不公。民主黨觀塘區社區主任梁翊婷表示，數名同事早前出席民政處舉辦的講座，獲悉以區議員名義，可致電處方預留表格，<span style=\"color: red;\">並先後以民主黨區議員鄭景陽的名義，訂取共2,000份，惟今日到觀塘民政處取件時，對方聲稱「上頭沒有柯打」，未有預留給該黨，但職員翻查電腦紀錄，卻找到該黨預留的資料，最終他們只能取得150份，分發數個觀塘區辦事處，每個辦事處只得數十份</span>。而且除觀塘區外，屯門也有類似情況，但因街坊需求極大，他們亦一早擺街站，為街坊填表，最終他們要動用區議員辦事處的資源，為街坊印表格，「花好多資源去幫個政府做嘢」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">梁又指，當時在處方辦事處看見職員已預留數箱表格，予民建聯觀塘區議員兼該區副主席洪錦鉉。梁批評當局安排不善，更質疑當局在資源短缺下，「都有先後次序，留畀建制先」。</span>"},{"pid":"66ff788585998ff86403af70938b12c123b37697","tid":990362,"uid":36901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:44:02.000Z","msg":"民政署就要自打紙印<br />\n建制狗就一箱箱咁預留<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eebc5a53f2367f9b9049755a379a80cf27d5974","tid":990362,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:44:13.000Z","msg":"只要上頭有柯打電腦冇紀錄都唔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac60107817e2c974d0f43b4810b8b197fdf19b5e","tid":990362,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:44:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8a577272809786f13e463bc4937c65ff2cd8e6","tid":990362,"uid":64374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:59:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b936c51ad9eb3d54343121229647a711b7aa1e8","tid":990362,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:00:03.000Z","msg":"自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98698ac18f2b45272de6ff9b7167c26ff89bcc15","tid":990362,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:01:18.000Z","msg":"Edith Leung<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}